      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，LoadBalancer之后是到NGINX吗？这里有个细节，LoadBalancer到NGINX这层应该标注成HTTP(Infra_IngressController)吧，表示IngressController这层基础设施？",
      "elements_involved": [
