      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是IngressController。然后NGINX内部有个路由决策的过程，需要根据Host或者ServerAlias来决定转发到哪个后端，这个得用loop表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
